data.description: Looking for a home with space?!  Look no more.  This beautiful home offers 5 bedrooms, two bathrooms, an open concept kitchen and living area with gorgeous natural light as well as a breakfast bar and formal dining area. The master bedroom is huge with a nice walk in closet and master bathroom with the jacuzzi tub and separate shower.  You'll also enjoy double vanities for extra space. The other bedrooms opposite the master share a hall bathroom and have a hall desk area for an office. Outside you have over an acre with two shops to store your lawn mower, or other equipment.  Call/text today for more info or with any questions.
